'.
WARNING:root:Pattern '<V>(.*)</V>' does not match string '<V lang="lav">to saka kundziņa, to gaspaž́iņa:</V>
'.
WARNING:root:Pattern '<V>(.*)</V>' does not match string '<V lang="lav">„Pūcitem vajagu pērena dabut,</V>
'.
WARNING:root:Pattern '<V>(.*)</V>' does not match string '<V lang="lav">kad viņš aizgāja neaicināta!“</V>
'.
WARNING:root:Pattern '<V>(.*)</V>' does not match string '<V lang="lav">2a. Ai ai zvirbuli, kad ņemsi sievu?</V>
'.
